        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You realize that not every situation should be solved with a gun. You're an intellectual as well as a warrior, solving problems logically and learning about the galaxy. You keep your mind sharp with formal education or self-guided study. When logic breaks down, you're always ready to fall back on your combat training.</p>\n<p>Choose either Diplomacy or Society. You become trained in the chosen skill and one Lore skill of your choice. When you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.class-features.Item.Armor Expertise], you gain expert proficiency in Diplomacy or Society (whichever you selected) and the Lore skill you selected. This increases to master proficiency when you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.class-features.Item.Armor Mastery], and to legendary proficiency when you gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.class-features.Item.Legendary Armor]. You also gain the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Oppressive Presence] action.</p>"
        },
